251
00:12:38,540 --> 00:12:41,400
 prijatelj ga stavio tu u Zagrebu

252
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:42,900
 na stočni vagon.

253
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:45,860
 Konje su tamo slali u Italiju,

254
00:12:45,860 --> 00:12:47,880
 jedu konjetinu.

255
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:52,740
