 Onda je dobio sponsorstvo u Kanadi

262
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:03,480
 od jednog fakulteta

263
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:06,340
 i došao je tamo 62.

264
00:13:06,340 --> 00:13:08,140
 U stvari, prostite,

265
00:13:08,140 --> 00:13:10,120
 on je 60. došao tamo.

266
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:10,720
 Nakon dvije godine,

267
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,820
 mi smo došli 62.

