00:13:11,820 --> 00:13:14,500
 I možda to je prvi jedni puta

269
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:16,060
 da smo bio u Beogradu.

270
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:18,100
 Tamo smo od moraličstva zavize van.

271
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:20,140
 Kako je to na tvoju mamu?

272
00:13:20,140 --> 00:13:24,700
 Svata zatvor, strah, mala djeca?

273
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:26,240
 Pa gledajte, moja baka,

274
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:28,040
