275
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:28,940
 nešto mu je baka,

276
00:13:28,940 --> 00:13:30,240
 ali sjećam se, bila je...

277
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,040
 Kako je zvala ona?

278
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:31,620
 Anica.

279
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:33,580
 Bila je Vedra.

280
00:13:33,580 --> 00:13:35,460
 Praktisirala je tu ona.

281
00:13:35,460 --> 00:13:37,080
 Ta obitle Živković,

282
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:38,160
