00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,420
 a tvoji su iz Posavine.

287
00:13:43,420 --> 00:13:44,520
 Iz Botsanske Posavine, da.

288
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:46,920
 To je bila najbogatija obitle

289
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:47,900
 30. godina.

290
00:13:47,900 --> 00:13:49,180
 Moj prabba,

291
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:50,880
 ovaj pradijed Nikola Živković,

292
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:51,880
 njega se zvali Gazda.

293
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:53,760
 Oni imali su tamo

294
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:55,220
