296
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:58,120
 Ja mislim, to je tisuć,

297
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,160
 jedan je dulom,

298
00:13:59,160 --> 00:14:01,160
 300 puta 10,

299
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:05,720
 onda bi oni imali su svinokolje.

300
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,680
 Bogati su bili,

301
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:08,880
 slali bi svinje tamo

302
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:09,920
 u svaki godine,

303
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:11,140
 u 11. mjesecu

304
00:14:11,140 --> 00:14:13,940
 u Mađarsku.

305
00:14:13,940 --> 00:14:15,480
 To je sve oduzeto

306
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:16,140
 nakon rata.

307
00:14:16,140 --> 00:14:18,100
 Ubili su,

308
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:20,380
 moja baka je na križnom putu,

309
00:14:20,380 --> 00:14:21,420
 svoje nečak je videla,

310
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:22,060
 njih su ubili.

311
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:23,760
 Matri su mi silovali

312
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:25,920
