313
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:27,300
 Dva puta je silovana,

314
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:28,160
 to moram reći,

315
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:29,080
 ta istina je istina.

316
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:30,500
 17 godina,

317
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:31,660
 o tome se ne govori,

318
00:14:31,660 --> 00:14:32,920
