326
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:43,340
 Samo ću vam opet ispričat,

327
00:14:43,340 --> 00:14:44,720
 kad sam spomenuo

328
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:45,920
 Josovo me,

329
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,540
 ovome,

330
00:14:47,540 --> 00:14:48,820
 Kovač,

331
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:49,680
