342
00:15:00,780 --> 00:15:01,840
 ja ne kopam po smeću.

343
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:03,520
 Oni se nikad ne mijenjaju.

344
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:04,760
 A vidite,

345
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:05,540
