347
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,400
 Znate,

348
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:09,980
 to me se ne priča.

349
00:15:09,980 --> 00:15:11,340
 Ali da se vratimo

350
00:15:11,340 --> 00:15:11,920
 samo na ovu tvoju.

351
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:12,700
 Da, na baku,

352
00:15:12,700 --> 00:15:13,180
 da, evo,

353
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:14,080
 baka joj isto.

354
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:14,740
 Dakle,

355
00:15:14,740 --> 00:15:15,000
 mama,

356
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:17,720
