359
00:15:20,180 --> 00:15:21,400
 Evo,

360
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:22,580
 mi nismo šest mjeseci,

361
00:15:22,580 --> 00:15:23,900
 imali nestale mjesec dana.

362
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:25,360
 Ti i brat,

363
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,280
 ste imali šest mjeseci,

364
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:27,220
 mama su zatvorili u zavu.

365
00:15:27,220 --> 00:15:27,460
 Da,

366
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:28,640
 mi smo spavali

367
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:30,060
 tri generacije od ovog zida.

368
00:15:30,060 --> 00:15:31,540
 Koliko je tu metara,

369
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:32,180
 tu dugi nini,

370
00:15:32,180 --> 00:15:32,860
 deset metara,

371
00:15:32,860 --> 00:15:33,440
 dvajst metara.

372
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:35,060
 Baka je spavala ovako,

373
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:35,620
 a mi ovako.

374
00:15:35,620 --> 00:15:37,980
 Onda su oduzeli svoje imovinu,

375
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:39,080
