00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,700
 da ne govorim sad,

377
00:15:40,700 --> 00:15:42,320
 toga svega.

378
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,500
 Imali su u stanu,

379
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:44,020
