380
00:15:44,020 --> 00:15:44,880
 u Sarajevo.

381
00:15:45,660 --> 00:15:46,280
 to je oduzeto.

382
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,860
 I onda,

383
00:15:47,860 --> 00:15:49,980
 oni su de facto

384
00:15:49,980 --> 00:15:51,340
 prisilili ljude da bježe.

385
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:52,540
 Znate,

386
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:53,440
 ali da,

387
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,740
