393
00:16:00,900 --> 00:16:02,560
 to je bio vojni zatvor Ozne.

394
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:04,120
 I šta su radili?

395
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:06,400
 Ljude bi ubili,

396
00:16:06,940 --> 00:16:08,060
 i onda dva tjedna kasnije

397
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:08,940
 je Xbox Fakto

398
00:16:08,940 --> 00:16:09,940
