00:16:09,940 --> 00:16:11,100
 Zašto?

400
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:11,940
 Dajmo dozu imovinu.

401
00:16:11,940 --> 00:16:13,560
 Ja se pitam,

402
00:16:13,560 --> 00:16:15,140
