 Stari Zagrebenesto

411
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:27,340
 gdje je Logor kanal.

412
00:16:27,340 --> 00:16:28,640
 Moj djede je bio tamo,

413
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:28,900
