414
00:16:28,900 --> 00:16:31,300
 Ne znamo u čim stanovima

415
00:16:31,300 --> 00:16:31,840
 žive nije i dvojica,

416
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:32,120
 Ne znam,

417
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:32,740
 ja se pitan.

418
00:16:32,740 --> 00:16:34,760
 To je pitanje,

419
00:16:34,760 --> 00:16:36,700
 retoričko pitanje.

420
00:16:36,700 --> 00:16:37,760
 Mogu postaviti pitanje

421
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:38,280
 i drugi.

422
00:16:38,280 --> 00:16:39,760
 Gdje je tamo

423
00:16:39,760 --> 00:16:40,760
 ovaj Logor kanal

424
00:16:40,760 --> 00:16:41,700
 bilo je šest baraka

425
00:16:41,700 --> 00:16:43,640
 i tamo je bilo

426
00:16:43,640 --> 00:16:44,720
 izgrađeno je

427
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,780
 41. do 45.

428
00:16:45,780 --> 00:16:46,680
 za društvenog,

429
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:46,940
 ne znam,

430
00:16:46,940 --> 00:16:47,860
 ove udruge.

