00:16:47,860 --> 00:16:49,180
 I tamo je,

432
00:16:49,180 --> 00:16:49,960
 ljude su odvodili,

433
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:50,480
 moj djete,

434
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,280
