444
00:17:02,140 --> 00:17:02,660
 vas nema.

445
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:03,260
 višta gotove.

446
00:17:03,260 --> 00:17:05,000
 Ali, na neki način

447
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,200
