451
00:17:10,820 --> 00:17:12,280
 u Titovoj Jugoslaviji

452
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:12,880
 nakon

453
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:14,120
 drugog svjetskog rata,

454
00:17:14,120 --> 00:17:14,380
 dakle,

455
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:15,680
 bez ratnih djelovanja,

456
00:17:15,680 --> 00:17:16,180
 bez ičega,

457
00:17:16,180 --> 00:17:17,580
 koji služi odmazdi.

458
00:17:17,580 --> 00:17:19,140
 Na neki način

459
00:17:19,140 --> 00:17:20,040
 sada si ti

460
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:20,800
