462
00:17:22,120 --> 00:17:23,060
 prošli kroz

463
00:17:23,060 --> 00:17:24,300
 određenu

464
00:17:24,300 --> 00:17:25,120
 kalvari

465
00:17:25,120 --> 00:17:25,560
 i opet sad

466
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:26,580
 u domovinskom ratu.

467
00:17:26,580 --> 00:17:27,180
 Ti si bio

468
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:28,420
 teško ranjen,

469
00:17:28,420 --> 00:17:29,540
 brat ti je bio

470
00:17:29,540 --> 00:17:30,600
 u Logoru mučen.

471
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,240
 kako to sve,

472
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:35,560
 kako to sve ti sad

473
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:36,680
