712
00:26:14,040 --> 00:26:16,440
 Ali, kad sam vidio te mlade dečke iz Hrvatske,

713
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:18,240
 iz Bosne i Zrcegovine, izvan Dijaspore,

714
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:21,260
 ta Bojno-Zrinski je bila jedinstvena jedna.

715
00:26:21,260 --> 00:26:24,160
 To je mikrokozmo bilo jedinstvena Hrvatska za mene.

716
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:27,060
 Ti, sjećam se, te dečke neki su poginuli.

717
00:26:27,060 --> 00:26:29,400
 Pravi, mladi dečki.

718
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:31,720
 I to je bilo, to je za mene bilo

719
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:34,360
 ostvareno jednog sna od kad sam to vidio.

720
00:26:34,360 --> 00:26:35,620
 Hrvatski grb.

721
00:26:35,620 --> 00:26:39,580
 I nevjerojatno je to da ti 45 godina

722
00:26:39,580 --> 00:26:41,600
 jedan takav sustav komunistički

723
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:43,160
 stalno laže,

724
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:45,140
 pritišće, progoni,

725
00:26:46,500 --> 00:26:48,920
 krivotvori i povijest i sadašnjost.

726
00:26:48,920 --> 00:26:50,480
 I onda ti opet iziđu,

727
00:26:50,480 --> 00:26:53,300
 padne Berlinski zidi,

728
00:26:53,300 --> 00:26:54,240
 opet ti iziđu neki

729
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:55,880
 novi ljudi, mladi,

730
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:57,280
 koji su rođeni u komunizmu,

731
00:26:57,280 --> 00:26:59,000
 a koji imaju dobru sliku u glavi,

732
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,080
 kako stvari izgledaju.

733
00:27:00,080 --> 00:27:01,600
 Pa, Bog je gospodar povijesti.

734
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:02,320
 I što je demokracija.

735
00:27:02,320 --> 00:27:03,820
 Da, Bog je gospodar povijesti.

736
00:27:03,820 --> 00:27:06,120
 Sada neko istina traži činjenice,

737
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:07,760
 ali ona je uvijek,

738
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:09,300
 uvijek ispljevana na videla.

739
00:27:09,300 --> 00:27:11,260
 To je najteža bitka,

740
00:27:11,260 --> 00:27:12,840
 jer što sam prije govorio,

741
00:27:12,840 --> 00:27:16,760
 da, možda pomeno samo Ciceron,

742
00:27:16,760 --> 00:27:18,940
 on je istinu govori,

743
00:27:18,940 --> 00:27:19,720
 bio u senatu,

744
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:20,860
 kako je završio.

745
00:27:20,860 --> 00:27:22,920
 Odrubili su mu glavu,

746
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:23,780
 nosili na kolsu,

747
00:27:23,780 --> 00:27:24,700
 na kopiju.

748
00:27:24,700 --> 00:27:25,980
 Ali on je uvijek,

749
00:27:25,980 --> 00:27:26,680
 rekao je da je

750
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:29,100
 u svakom društvu,

751
00:27:29,100 --> 00:27:30,080
 to se nije promijenilo,

752
00:27:30,720 --> 00:27:32,200
 kad vi branite svoj grad,

753
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:33,440
 kad vidite izvan zidina,

754
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:35,160
 koliko ima manipula,

755
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,160
 kohorti, legija,

756
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:37,620
 neprite konjanika,

757
00:27:37,620 --> 00:27:38,220
 vidite ga.

758
00:27:38,220 --> 00:27:40,480
 Ali neprite koji je onutar zidinja,

759
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:43,220
 koji podkopava temelje grada po noći,

760
00:27:43,220 --> 00:27:44,840
 kaže, njega se morate bojati

761
00:27:44,840 --> 00:27:45,740
 više od ubojice.

762
00:27:45,740 --> 00:27:46,920
 To je naš problem.

763
00:27:46,920 --> 00:27:52,780
 Ostalo je ta mentalna baština komunizma,

764
00:27:52,780 --> 00:27:54,780
 koja je razarajuća za duh i za umove.

765
00:27:54,780 --> 00:27:58,280
 A glavna taktika njove je manipulacija

766
00:27:58,280 --> 00:27:59,980
 i laž.

767
00:27:59,980 --> 00:28:02,540
 Samo bi spomenuo da imamo ljudi.

768
00:28:02,540 --> 00:28:04,300
 Spomenuo bi, na primjer,

769
00:28:04,300 --> 00:28:05,480
 ako smijem,

770
00:28:05,480 --> 00:28:07,660
 jednu našu mladu povješničarku.

771
00:28:07,660 --> 00:28:09,940
 Prga va je udara.

772
00:28:09,940 --> 00:28:16,060
 I to društvo povješničara Rudolf Horvat,

773
00:28:16,060 --> 00:28:17,660
 koja je raskrinkala ovu...

774
00:28:17,660 --> 00:28:18,480
 Jasenovac.

775
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:20,300
 Taj mito Jasenovcu.

776
00:28:20,300 --> 00:28:23,020
 Da, i Blanko Matković,

777
00:28:23,020 --> 00:28:23,660
 koja je napisala

778
00:28:23,660 --> 00:28:24,960
 pet, čest knjiga

779
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:26,220
 u stvijepel od istraživanja.

780
00:28:26,220 --> 00:28:28,060
 Ona je studijena na Vorovic koleđu.

781
00:28:29,100 --> 00:28:30,360
 Širinja šu istinu vani,

782
00:28:30,360 --> 00:28:31,740
 ali piše na engleskom jeziku.

783
00:28:31,740 --> 00:28:32,260
 Znate.

784
00:28:32,260 --> 00:28:34,640
 I sad ima promociju knjige

785
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:35,680
 u petom mjesecu.

786
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:38,800
 I ljudi su neki čitali njezne knjige

787
00:28:38,800 --> 00:28:40,440
 i vidi tamo oca, vidi.

788
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:41,220
 U represiji,

789
00:28:41,220 --> 00:28:42,620
 koji je bijen možda nakon rata

790
00:28:42,620 --> 00:28:43,960
 u Mjimovskoj krajini.

791
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:45,000
 Znate.

792
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,980
 I ona, ona, ona...

793
00:28:46,980 --> 00:28:48,860
 Oklasi, nisam te ovo sad razumijela što si...

794
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:49,880
 Kako miš vidio oca?

795
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:52,460
 Oca je ona napisala monografije.

796
00:28:52,460 --> 00:28:52,800
 Dobro.

797
00:28:52,800 --> 00:28:54,360
 Partizanski zločini nakon,

798
00:28:54,360 --> 00:28:55,380
 rečem Mjimovska krajina,

799
00:28:55,380 --> 00:28:56,880
 Damatinsko Zagorije,

800
00:28:57,280 --> 00:28:57,940
 i tako dalje.

801
00:28:57,940 --> 00:28:59,420
 Bave sa tim...

802
00:28:59,420 --> 00:29:00,540
 Dakle, neki ljudi su ostili

803
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:01,900
 za svoju obitelj.

804
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:03,020
 Gdje su bijeni njihovi?

805
00:29:03,020 --> 00:29:03,980
 Da, što je prešućeno.

806
00:29:03,980 --> 00:29:06,260
 Ali ono što je doista nevjerojatno,

807
00:29:06,260 --> 00:29:08,280
 de facto, u posljednjih,

808
00:29:08,280 --> 00:29:10,060
 ja bih rekla, desetak godina,

809
00:29:10,060 --> 00:29:12,400
 koliko su ta istraživanja,

810
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:14,100
 povijesna, neovisna,

811
00:29:14,100 --> 00:29:16,880
 napravljena lege artis

812
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:18,700
 u skladu sa istinom i strukom,

813
00:29:18,700 --> 00:29:20,000
 koliko su sad u stvari

814
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:21,900
 cijeli taj mit o Jesenovcu,

815
00:29:21,900 --> 00:29:24,240
 je potpuno svakom jasno da je mit.

816
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:26,400
 Da, ali nije samo, vidite, nije samo...

817
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:28,080
 Lažne brojke, o tome govorimo.

818
00:29:28,080 --> 00:29:30,520
 To imate, znate, ona tri popisa

819
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:31,600
 famozna nakon rata.

820
00:29:31,600 --> 00:29:32,940
 Ma da, ali sada te kalkulacije,

821
00:29:32,940 --> 00:29:34,240
 da, koje su napravljene.

822
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:35,580
 Da, i to što sam rekao,

823
00:29:35,580 --> 00:29:36,460
 što je rekao, Orwell,

824
00:29:36,460 --> 00:29:37,880
 prošlost nikad nije prošla.

825
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:38,900
 Vidite, mi se ne smijemo

826
00:29:38,900 --> 00:29:39,920
 bavati prošlošću.

827
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:40,440
 Da, da, da.

828
00:29:40,440 --> 00:29:41,840
 Ako mogu Srbi,

829
00:29:41,840 --> 00:29:42,900
 može Srpska pravljena crkva.

830
00:29:42,900 --> 00:29:44,280
 Svi se mogu osim nas, da.

831
00:29:44,280 --> 00:29:44,820
 Osim nas.

832
00:29:44,820 --> 00:29:46,200
 Onda nemojmo se vraćati,

833
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:46,860
 pa ne, trebamo se vraćati.

834
00:29:46,860 --> 00:29:47,960
 Da, oni se boje istine.

835
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:48,300
 Da.

836
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:57,960
 Pa gledajte,

837
00:29:57,960 --> 00:29:59,380
 ljude koje sam spomenu

838
00:29:59,380 --> 00:30:01,220
 su ubijeni nakon 45.

839
00:30:01,220 --> 00:30:02,780
 Pa da, u miru.

840
00:30:02,780 --> 00:30:04,060
 Da, Hrvatsi i Tjedniki.

841
00:30:04,060 --> 00:30:05,100
 Ja sam našao spisak

842
00:30:05,100 --> 00:30:07,180
 900 skoro ljudi,

843
00:30:07,180 --> 00:30:08,680
 curice 17 godina,

844
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:09,840
 ubijeni, streljani

845
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:11,120
 od 45. svibnja,

846
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:13,540
 kad su ušli ovi banditi

847
00:30:13,540 --> 00:30:14,060
 u Zagreb,

848
00:30:14,060 --> 00:30:15,600
 do 46. godine.

849
00:30:15,600 --> 00:30:17,020
 Da, ali ono što,

850
00:30:17,020 --> 00:30:19,560
 samo da sad povežemo

851
00:30:19,560 --> 00:30:20,680
 s ovim što si htio reći

852
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:22,760
 o ovim istraživanjima,

853
00:30:22,760 --> 00:30:23,960
 htio si, rekao si gospodinu,

854
00:30:23,960 --> 00:30:25,380
 Matković i druge.

855
00:30:25,380 --> 00:30:27,240
 Što si tu htio završiti

856
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:28,040
 samo oko toga?

857
00:30:28,040 --> 00:30:28,960
 To se piše,

858
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,520
 a mi moramo to istinu

859
00:30:30,520 --> 00:30:31,400
 plasirati van.

860
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:33,700
 Ja pitam naša diplomate,

861
00:30:33,700 --> 00:30:34,800
 recimo, ne samo,

862
00:30:34,800 --> 00:30:36,680
 nisu samo zakazali

863
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,340
 kad je u pitanje

864
00:30:37,340 --> 00:30:38,680
 gospodarska diplomacija.

865
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:40,540
 Da, to su sigurno.

866
00:30:40,540 --> 00:30:41,520
 Po kojoj sumamo ovde

867
00:30:41,520 --> 00:30:42,780
 Greenfield-unistice?

868
00:30:42,780 --> 00:30:43,520
 Nema ih.

869
00:30:43,520 --> 00:30:45,520
 Ali oni ne smiju se,

870
00:30:45,520 --> 00:30:46,000
 ovaj,

871
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,600
 ja direkt idem ljudima,

872
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:48,780
 ako mogu samo ispričati

873
00:30:48,780 --> 00:30:49,980
 jednu kratku priču.

874
00:30:49,980 --> 00:30:51,680
 Došli su tu ovaj

875
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:52,300
 nizozemci

876
00:30:52,300 --> 00:30:53,360
 nakon Praljkova.

877
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:54,400
 smrti.

878
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:55,920
 Pred sabor.

879
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:56,500
 Sad,

880
00:30:56,500 --> 00:30:57,920
 ja da nije imao vremena

881
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:59,000
 s njima razgovarati,

882
00:30:59,000 --> 00:30:59,860
 pošto govorim engleski,

883
00:30:59,860 --> 00:31:00,720
 s njima sam razgovarao.

884
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:02,420
 Oni su odmah počeli,

885
00:31:02,420 --> 00:31:03,100
 šta mi ste...

886
00:31:03,100 --> 00:31:03,680
 Televizija.

887
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:04,800
 Televizija iz Nizozemske,

888
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:05,640
 iz Amsterdam-a.

889
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:08,220
 Odmah Praljak,

890
00:31:08,220 --> 00:31:09,280
 zločenac,

891
00:31:09,280 --> 00:31:09,520
 kažem,

892
00:31:09,520 --> 00:31:10,280
 čekajte malo,

893
00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:11,680
 da ja vas pitam jednu stvar.

894
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:13,740
 jeste vi formirali

895
00:31:13,740 --> 00:31:14,640
 komisiju

896
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:15,440
 za pomrijebu

897
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:15,800
 u istinu

898
00:31:15,800 --> 00:31:16,420
 između vać

899
00:31:16,420 --> 00:31:17,420
 i Indonezije.

900
00:31:17,420 --> 00:31:19,100
 Što ja razumijem,

901
00:31:19,100 --> 00:31:21,020
 vi ste u Indoneziju

902
00:31:21,020 --> 00:31:22,000
 19. stoljeća,

903
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:23,520
 vi ste prva kolonijna sila,

904
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:24,420
 koja mi je

905
00:31:24,420 --> 00:31:25,600
 Traljezi upotrbljavala

906
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:27,860
 protiv otovanih stanovništva.

907
00:31:28,380 --> 00:31:30,060
 i vi ste dok ste izašli iz Indonezije,

908
00:31:30,060 --> 00:31:32,320
 gdje ste se borili sa Englezima

909
00:31:32,320 --> 00:31:33,480
 protiv Indonezije,

910
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:34,560
 to je njihova zemlja,

911
00:31:34,560 --> 00:31:36,280
 koju ste vi kolonizirali,

912
00:31:36,280 --> 00:31:38,640
 imate na internetu

913
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:39,160
 pisma,

914
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:40,000
 poručnika,

915
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:40,680
 satnika,

916
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,080
 zapovjede,

917
00:31:42,080 --> 00:31:43,460
 izazemskog,

918
00:31:43,460 --> 00:31:44,580
 bojšći,

919
00:31:44,580 --> 00:31:45,800
 palite sela,

920
00:31:45,800 --> 00:31:46,820
 ubijajte kako odbiježi.

921
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:47,720
 To ste vi.

922
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:48,640
 Kažem,

923
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:49,840
 kad ste vi ukonili ropstvo?

924
00:31:49,840 --> 00:31:52,900
 1863. godine.

925
00:31:52,900 --> 00:31:55,100
 Tamo se Crnce u Corinamu

926
00:31:55,100 --> 00:31:56,180
 stavljara nekao,

927
00:31:56,180 --> 00:31:57,540
 znate šta su Čengile.

928
00:31:58,380 --> 00:32:00,440
 kad imate svinokolje,

929
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:00,980
 kuka,

930
00:32:00,980 --> 00:32:02,620
 imate sliku,

931
00:32:02,620 --> 00:32:03,320
 William Blake,

932
00:32:03,320 --> 00:32:04,180
 kršćanin,

933
00:32:04,180 --> 00:32:05,300
 Englez je bio kršćanin,

934
00:32:05,300 --> 00:32:06,020
 ali je bio kršćanin,

935
00:32:06,020 --> 00:32:07,140
 slika Crnca,

936
00:32:07,140 --> 00:32:08,900
 ispod rebara,

937
00:32:08,900 --> 00:32:09,560
 nabijena kuka,

938
00:32:09,560 --> 00:32:10,480
 visiko komad mesa.

939
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:11,740
 Kaže, to ste vi radili.

940
00:32:11,740 --> 00:32:13,440
 Ako vas zanimaju zločnici,

941
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:14,860
 otižite možda u Belgiju tu,

942
00:32:14,860 --> 00:32:16,840
 otvorite arhive za Belgijski Kongo,

943
00:32:16,840 --> 00:32:18,480
 gdje od 1885.

944
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:20,600
 u razmih od 20 godine

945
00:32:20,600 --> 00:32:22,140
 je bilo oko 1,5 milijona Crnaca

946
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:24,420
 od kralja Leopolda i ljudi.

947
00:32:24,420 --> 00:32:25,380
 Nemojte nama dolaziti.

948
00:32:25,380 --> 00:32:26,440
 Doviđenja.

949
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:27,760
 I što ste odgovorili?

950
00:32:27,760 --> 00:32:29,140
 O, pa onda kažem,

951
00:32:29,140 --> 00:32:30,100
 hvala, doviđenja.

952
00:32:30,100 --> 00:32:31,080
 Pa ne samo to,

953
00:32:31,080 --> 00:32:31,840
 pa možemo razgovarati

954
00:32:31,840 --> 00:32:33,220
 o nizuzemcima i srebrenici

955
00:32:33,220 --> 00:32:34,260
 ako trebamo i o tome.

956
00:32:34,260 --> 00:32:35,620
 Možemo razgovarati

957
00:32:35,620 --> 00:32:37,360
 o evakuacijama djece

958
00:32:37,360 --> 00:32:39,520
 koje su odbijane iz Sarajeva.

959
00:32:39,520 --> 00:32:41,160
 Da, ali sad za...

960
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:42,200
 Pošto mi ne znamo,

961
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,560
 većina ljudi ne zna

962
00:32:43,560 --> 00:32:44,580
 te činjenice.

963
00:32:44,580 --> 00:32:46,000
 Gledajte,

964
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:47,840
 pomenuo sam sad 47. godine

965
00:32:47,840 --> 00:32:48,720
 u bojstu civila

966
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:50,360
 u jednom selu u Indoneziji.

967
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:51,500
 I sad gledajte.

968
00:32:51,820 --> 00:32:52,540
 To je zataškano,

969
00:32:52,540 --> 00:32:53,340
 totalno bilo

970
00:32:53,340 --> 00:32:54,660
 u ovi njihov veterani

971
00:32:54,660 --> 00:32:55,160
 se digli.

972
