 još imam.

2057
00:55:52,820 --> 00:55:55,340
 On je umirao od raka

2058
00:55:55,340 --> 00:55:56,420
 i on je formirao,

2059
00:55:56,420 --> 00:55:57,200
 on vidio je kako čovjek

2060
00:55:57,200 --> 00:55:58,120
 jede iz Kante

2061
00:55:58,120 --> 00:55:58,960
 u Malom Gradiću,

2062
00:55:58,960 --> 00:55:59,840
 u Indienapolesu,

2063
00:55:59,840 --> 00:56:00,320
 u Americi.

2064
00:56:00,320 --> 00:56:02,100
 On je organizirao

2065
00:56:02,100 --> 00:56:03,080
 pučku kuhinju.

2066
00:56:03,080 --> 00:56:04,480
 On umire,

2067
00:56:04,480 --> 00:56:04,800
 dječko,

2068
00:56:04,800 --> 00:56:05,480
 13 godina,

2069
00:56:05,480 --> 00:56:05,920
 i kaže,

2070
00:56:05,920 --> 00:56:07,460
 ja sam ispunil svoju,

2071
00:56:07,460 --> 00:56:08,600
 mislio bi ispunite svoju.

2072
00:56:08,600 --> 00:56:09,940
 Ko smo mi?

2073
00:56:09,940 --> 00:56:11,580
 Da bi odustajali

2074
00:56:11,580 --> 00:56:12,640
 od djelovanja.

2075
00:56:12,640 --> 00:56:14,020
 Kada djete mora voditi,

2076
00:56:14,020 --> 00:56:14,800
 13 godina,

2077
00:56:14,800 --> 00:56:15,440
 podučiti,

2078
00:56:15,440 --> 00:56:16,360
 pa da.

2079
00:56:16,360 --> 00:56:17,560
 Ali zato je li si skroman,

2080
00:56:17,560 --> 00:56:18,480
 pa si spreman učiti

2081
00:56:18,480 --> 00:56:19,300
 od svakoga, da.

2082
00:56:19,300 --> 00:56:19,800
 Ne, a ne treba.

2083
00:56:19,800 --> 00:56:21,220
 Kukanje zabranjen.

2084
00:56:25,340 --> 00:56:26,600
 i pozdravljam vas

2085
00:56:26,600 --> 00:56:27,520
 do sljedećeg prilike.

2086
00:56:27,520 --> 00:56:56,380
 Hvala što pratite.

